ocs site generation logic. This ensures that the planner's consolidation algorithms and the builder's site scaffolding workflows are robust, deterministic, and produce high-quality documentation sites."},"2697":{"id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance-24","page_id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance#overview","content":"The planner logic determines how source files and symbols are grouped into documentation \"buckets,\" when to split or merge topics, and how to organize navigation. The builder logic takes these plans and generates a Fumadocs-compatible site scaffold, including handling OpenAPI assets, custom index pages, and special components."},"2698":{"id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance-25","page_id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance#overview","content":"This QA layer is critical for:"},"2699":{"id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance-26","page_id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance#overview","content":"Ensuring documentation is organized logically and consistently."},"2700":{"id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance-27","page_id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance#overview","content":"Preventing accidental merges or splits of important topics (e.g., not merging API endpoint docs)."},"2701":{"id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance-28","page_id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance#overview","content":"Guaranteeing site builds are reproducible and handle edge cases (e.g., custom index pages, OpenAPI presence/absence)."},"2702":{"id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance-29","page_id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance#overview","content":"Maintaining compatibility with Fumadocs and DeepDoc's custom MDX conventions."},"2703":{"id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance-30","page_id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance#overview","content":"For a high-level view of DeepDoc's architecture, see DeepDoc Architecture & Overview. For the builder's integration with the frontend, see Frontend Documentation Site Builder. For the overall document generation pipeline, see Pipeline: Document Generation & Planning."},"2704":{"id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance-31","page_id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance#files-covered","content":"File Path"},"2705":{"id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance-32","page_id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance#files-covered","content":"Role"},"2706":{"id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance-33","page_id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance#files-covered","content":"Key Symbols"},"2707":{"id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance-34","page_id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance#files-covered","content":"Responsibility"},"2708":{"id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance-35","page_id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance#files-covered","content":"tests/test_planner_consolidation.py"},"2709":{"id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance-36","page_id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance#files-covered","content":"Handler/Test"},"2710":{"id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance-37","page_id":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/planner-builder-quality-assurance#files-covered","content":"_make_scan, _make_bucket, test_should_